Package genetic_algorithm.factory

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GeneticConfigurationFactory
    GeneticAlgorithmRunner is the main class to perform all the operations This class is the implementation of factory design pattern which handles the instantiation (creation) of the different Selection, Reproduction (/Crossover) or Mutation objects.
    GeneticFactory
    This is the GeneticFactory class which is the Abstract factory pattern and this is the place where the user communicate to and asks for a specific version of a Genetic algorithm.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    GeneticConfigurationFactory.OperationType
    This method will generate a new class of one of the crossover classes that are for this genetic configuration setup.
    GeneticConfigurationFactory.PointType
